<a href="https://requires.io/github/pydanny/cookiecutter-django/requirements/?branch=master"><img alt="Requirements Status" src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/8f42138d363b24e1213f6328b78c5e68fc8cc524/68747470733a2f2f72657175697265732e696f2f6769746875622f707964616e6e792f636f6f6b69656375747465722d646a616e676f2f726571756972656d656e74732e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572" data-canonical-src="https://requires.io/github/pydanny/cookiecutter-django/requirements.svg?branch=master" style="max-width:100%;"></a>
